{"type":"message","id":"84614a9e","parentId":"f3d69613","timestamp":"2026-02-18T09:41:03.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"   Now let me create today's memory file with the reference","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"          functions.write:33","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-02-18.md","content":"# 2026-02-18 - Daily Notes\n\n## Morning\n\n### 7:08 AM — Gateway Token Issue\n- User reported missing 7 AM daily ping (cron job)\n- Investigated: **device token mismatch** in gateway auth\n- **Root cause:** systemd service had stale token in memory from previous config update\n- **Fix:** `systemctl --user daemon-reload && systemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway.service`\n- Gateway now healthy, RPC probe: ok\n- Cron system operational, but missed today's run\n\n### 9:53 AM — Manual Daily Ping Trigger\n- Gateway confirmed operational\n- Fetched Bitcoin: $67,078 (↓2.51%)\n- Fetched stock prices: NVDA $184.98, MSFT $396.79, GOOGL $302.01, INTC $46.21, META $639.27, AMD $203.04\n- Fetched GitHub top repos via API\n- Sent daily ping to Telegram topic 1087368827 ✅\n\n### 10:44 AM — Config Update Requested\n- User requested to lock all API calls to NVIDIA provider only\n- Updated `/home/pete/.openclaw/openclaw.json`:\n  - Removed other auth profiles (openai, moonshot, openrouter)\n  - Retained only `nvidia:default` provider\n  - Kept existing NVIDIA config with moonshotai/kimi-k2.5 model\n- Still need to restart gateway to apply changes\n\n---\n\n## Afternoon\n\n### 4:18 PM — Persona & Skills Recap\n- User requested full persona recap\n- **WHOAMI.md created:** `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/WHOAMI.md`\n  - Core persona (lobster energy, direct communication, actual opinions)\n  - Roles (trusty assistant, coding assistant, frontend architect, proactive operator)\n  - Standard Operating Procedure (ANALYZE → PLAN → VALIDATE → IMPLEMENT → VERIFY → DELIVER)\n  - Skills inventory: ~125 skills across categories + 11 knowledge work plugins\n\n### 5:05 PM — PRD Understanding Request\n- User requested analysis of `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/PRD.md`\n- **UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md created:** `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md`\n  - Architecture philosophy (SQLite, vectors, Telegram-first)\n  - CRM system deep dive (~1,174 contacts, 16 intent types, discovery pipeline)\n  - Skills inventory (22 installed + 2 preview)\n  - Critical tools (cron-log, business-meta-analysis, social-tracker)\n  - Database inventory (15+ databases)\n  - Cron jobs (30+ scheduled tasks)\n  - Key operational patterns\n\n---\n\n## Reference Files Created Today\n\n| File | Purpose | Location |\n|------|---------|----------|\n| **WHOAMI.md** | Persona, roles, responsibilities, skills inventory | `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/WHOAMI.md` |\n| **UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md** | Architecture guide, CRM system, operational patterns | `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md` |\n\n---\n\n## Pending Items\n\n- [ ] Restart gateway to apply NVIDIA-only config changes\n- [ ] Verify daily ping resumes tomorrow (7 AM Asia/Singapore)\n\n---\n\n*Written by trusty-pal 🤝🦞*\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":61573,"output":820,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62393,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771407584432}}
