{"type":"message","id":"9b9faa6f","parentId":"9a66aac4","timestamp":"2026-02-19T01:46:16.796Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"203\",\n  \"sender\": \"1087368827\"\n}\n```\n\nI prefer the following format where I get the delta in price over the past 1 day. 📈 Crypto • Bitcoin: $68,054 (📉 -1.28%) 💹 Tech Stocks • NVDA $182.81 (📉 -2.21%) • MSFT $401.32 (📉 -0.13%) • GOOGL $305.72 (📉 -1.06%) • INTC $46.79 (📈 +0.67%) • META $639.77 (📉 -1.55%) • AMD $207.32 (📈 +0.67%) ⭐ Top 5 GitHub Repos by Stars 1. build-your-own-x — Master programming by recreating favorites (466.6K ⭐) 2. awesome — Curated lists of interesting topics (438K ⭐) 3. freeCodeCamp — [freeCodeCamp.org](http://freecodecamp.org/)'s open-source curriculum (437.1K ⭐) 4. public-apis — Collective list of free APIs (398.8K ⭐) 5. free-programming-books — Freely available programming books (382.6K ⭐)"}],"timestamp":1771465576787}}
{"type":"message","id":"f6eb1c4d","parentId":"9b9faa6f","timestamp":"2026-02-19T01:47:58.102Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user wants me to update the daily ping format to match their preference. They've shown me a specific format they want. Let me update the cron job payload","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" Will update the cron job payload with your preferred format. This means I'll need to: 1. Fetch Bitcoin with 24h change 2. Fetch stocks with 24h change (or calculate from previous close) 3. Format with delta arrows (📈📉) 4. Include GitHub repos with descriptions in K format 5. Update the"},{"type":"toolCall","id":" functions.cron:79","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"10a19bb7-7afb-4b24-8478-62555b540c2d","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Send the daily ping to Telegram (ID: 1087368827) with this exact format:\n\n📈 Crypto\n• Bitcoin: $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n\n💹 Tech Stocks\n• NVDA $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• MSFT $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• GOOGL $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• INTC $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• META $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• AMD $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n\n⭐ Top 5 GitHub Repos by Stars\n1. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n2. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n3. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n4. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n5. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n\nFetch:\n1) Bitcoin from CoinGecko API: https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true (show price and 24h change % with 📉 for negative, 📈 for positive)\n2) Stocks using yfinance with 1d history to calculate day-over-day change: NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD (show 📈/📉 + delta)\n3) GitHub repos: https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=stars:>1000&sort=stars&order=desc&per_page=5 (format stars as K, e.g., 466.6K, include descriptions)\n\nSend via message tool to Telegram target 1087368827.","thinking":"low","timeoutSeconds":900}}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":118231,"output":580,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118811,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771465576792}}
