lastDurationMs\": 300204,\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 3,\n    \"lastError\": \"Error: Unknown model: xai/grok-4-1-fast-reasoning\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"10a19bb7-7afb-4b24-8478-62555b540c2d","agentId":"main","name":"daily-ping-telegram","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1770773359648,"updatedAtMs":1771465678146,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 7 * * *","tz":"Asia/Singapore"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Send the daily ping to Telegram (ID: 1087368827) with this exact format:\n\n📈 Crypto\n• Bitcoin: $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n\n💹 Tech Stocks\n• NVDA $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• MSFT $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• GOOGL $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• INTC $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• META $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n• AMD $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n\n⭐ Top 5 GitHub Repos by Stars\n1. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n2. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n3. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n4. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n5. NAME — DESCRIPTION (STARS ⭐)\n\nFetch:\n1) Bitcoin from CoinGecko API: https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true (show price and 24h change % with 📉 for negative, 📈 for positive)\n2) Stocks using yfinance with 1d history to calculate day-over-day change: NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD (show 📈/📉 + delta)\n3) GitHub repos: https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=stars:>1000&sort=stars&order=desc&per_page=5 (format stars as K, e.g., 466.6K, include descriptions)\n\nSend via message tool to Telegram target 1087368827.","thinking":"low","timeoutSeconds":900},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1771542000000,"lastRunAtMs":1771465038516,"lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":300204,"consecutiveErrors":3,"lastError":"Error: Unknown model: xai/grok-4-1-fast-reasoning"}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771465678151}}
