{"type":"message","id":"46dcb752","parentId":"f501753b","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:14:41.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📅 Daily Ping — Sunday, February 22, 2026\n\n💰 Bitcoin\n• Price: $67,975 USD\n• 24h: -0.21% 📉\n\n📊 Tech Stocks\n• NVDA: $189.82 (+1.02%) 📈\n• MSFT: $397.23 (-0.31%) 📉\n• GOOGL: $314.98 (+4.01%) 📈\n• INTC: $44.11 (-1.14%) 📉\n• META: $655.66 (+1.69%) 📈\n• AMD: $200.15 (-1.58%) 📉\n\n🚀 Trending GitHub Repos (Created Since 2024)\n1. openclaw/openclaw ⭐ 216.2K\n2. x1xhlol/system-prompts-and-models-of-ai-tools ⭐ 115.6K\n3. deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3 ⭐ 101.7K\n4. google-gemini/gemini-cli ⭐ 95.2K\n5. microsoft/markitdown ⭐ 87.5K\n6. punkpeye/awesome-mcp-servers ⭐ 81.3K\n7. github/spec-kit ⭐ 71.0K\n8. openai/codex ⭐ 61.3K\n9. docling-project/docling ⭐ 53.8K\n10. Zie619/n8n-workflows ⭐ 51.9K\n\n—\n⏰ 07:10 SGT | Data: CoinGecko, Yahoo Finance, GitHub API"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771715681088}}
